Package: trendsinpapers
Type: Package
Title: Loads, Cleans and Analyses .RES Files of Academic Publications
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sam", "Abbott", email = "contact@samabbott.co.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Cleans and munges a .RES file of academic papers. Using this standard  format, simple analysis functions
        allow trends in publications over time to be investigated, and the relationships between authors are visualised. A literature review
        of dynamic TB models is used as an example.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat,
          knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
URL: http://www.samabbott.co.uk/trendsinpapers,
        https://github.com/seabbs/trendsinpapers
BugReports: https://github.com/seabbs/trendsinpapers/issues
VignetteBuilder: knitr
